OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FWhitehaven's rugby game with Goole
OL,8,FVikings was delayed as bomb disposal
OL,9,Fexperts were called to deal with what
OL,10,Fturned out to be a replica grenade.
OL,12,FKick-off at Victoria Pleasure Grounds
OL,13,Fwas delayed by 80 minutes on Sunday
OL,14,FApril 12 following the discovery next
OL,15,Fto the pitch.
OL,17,FThe immediate area was later secured
OL,18,Fand the scene declared safe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FWhitehaven's 36-22 win saw them swap
OL,8,Fplaces with Goole, who drop to 18th in
OL,9,Fthe Championship.
OL,11,FGoole Vikings said in a club
OL,12,Fstatement: "Following routine pre-
OL,13,Fmatch safety inspections, carried out
OL,14,Fas part of the club's standard
OL,15,Fmatchday operations prior to gates
OL,16,Fopening to spectators, an
OL,17,Funidentified, potentially explosive
OL,18,Fitem was discovered by the club's
OL,19,Fground safety team.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"Contrary to some external reports,
OL,8,Fthe item was located away from areas
OL,9,Faccessible to supporters and staff.
OL,10,FHowever, due to its nature and
OL,11,Fproximity to a scheduled event, the
OL,12,Fclub immediately activated its
OL,13,Festablished emergency protocols.
OL,15,F"This process was led by the club's
OL,16,Fground safety officer, in coordination
OL,17,Fwith the matchday stewarding team and
OL,18,Fboard of directors.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"The immediate area was secured, and
OL,8,FHumberside Police, the local authority
OL,9,Fand the Rugby Football League were
OL,10,Fcontacted without delay.
OL,12,F"The stadium remained under controlled
OL,13,Flockdown until specialist officers
OL,14,Ffrom the regional Explosive Ordnance
OL,15,FDisposal unit attended the site to
OL,16,Fassess the item.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"Following a full assessment, the
OL,8,Fdevice was confirmed to be a non-
OL,9,Fexplosive replica grenade and was
OL,10,Fsafely removed, with no further action
OL,11,Frequired."
OL,13,FGoole Vikings said the response from
OL,14,Fall parties was "swift, coordinated
OL,15,Fand highly professional" and that
OL,16,F"disruption was kept to a minimum".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FThe club added: "The incident
OL,8,Fdemonstrated the effectiveness of the
OL,9,Fclub's robust safety and operational
OL,10,Fprocedures, ensuring that the welfare
OL,11,Fof supporters, players, staff and
OL,12,Fpartners remained the absolute
OL,13,Fpriority at all times.
OL,15,F"While this was an unprecedented
OL,16,Fincident, the Victoria Pleasure
OL,17,FGrounds remains a safe and secure
OL,18,Fvenue.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776265866
OL,3,CBomb disposal experts delay
OL,4,CWhitehaven's victorious rugby league
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"Incidents of this nature are
OL,8,Fextremely rare, but Sunday's response
OL,9,Freflects the high standards of
OL,10,Fplanning, governance and safety
OL,11,Fmanagement that underpin matchday
OL,12,Foperations at the club."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
